# Torch7/Lua Model Scanner
Output demos/torch7-scan.gif
Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1400
Set Height 900
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 35ms

Type "setopt INTERACTIVE_COMMENTS"
Enter
Sleep 200ms

Type "export PYTHONPATH=$PWD/python"
Enter
Sleep 300ms

Type "echo '━━━ Torch7/Lua Malicious Model Scanner ━━━'"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "sentinel artifact /tmp/gif_fixtures/malicious_model.t7"
Enter
Sleep 4s

Sleep 2s
